Items.mt: There are all kinds of shows here! There are blowing, dancing, acrobatics, fiddling, winning flowers, mud balls, drum boards, throwing pots, flower bullets, cuju, tea sharing, water fiddling, stepping on mixed woods, dialing pots, miscellaneous arts, scattered juggling, folk singing, resting instruments, teaching aquatic birds, water puppets, strained water juggling, fireworks, starting wheels, walking lines, shooting stars, water bursts, kites, the list is endless, so if you have a favorite show, ask us and we will tell you when to start performing.
